INSTALLATION

In order to install the script do the following:

1. Create a new MySQL database for the application and add an user to it

2. Import the database blocker.sql to the newly created database

3. Extract Ips-Blacklist-Manager.zip to the directory which will be used for the application

4. Edit the file app/config/database.php and set it with your MySQL user and password

5. Get a Recaptcha key pair and add them to:

app/controllers/components/recaptcha.php

6. Finally, you can log in with:

user: admin
password: 1a1a1a
